56afb687-0b2e-4403-b59e-cc6911e5a41a.318f2aa6-9522-4709-95c5-75b33490aa4a.description=
Iterates through a list of values. If the list changes while running, the updates will be appended to the list.

Inputs\:
separator - The list separator (or delimiter).
list - The list to be split

Responses\:
has more - Another value was in the list, and has been returned.
failure - failed to process the list.
no more - The iterator has gone fully through the list. This response will only be returned once per iteration through the list, a subsequent call to the Iterator will restart the Iteration through the list.

Returns\:
The current element of the list, if the response is has more
56afb687-0b2e-4403-b59e-cc6911e5a41a.3275e702-6833-4d54-892f-0575d7cf1c67.description=Sorts a list. If this list is all numerical, it is sorted in numerical order, other wise it is sorted in alphabetical order. 
Inputs\:
list - The list to be processed
delimiter - The list delimiter.
reverse - A boolean value, sort the list in reverse order?

Returns\:
The sorted list.

Responses\:
success - operation completed
failure - something went wrong.
56afb687-0b2e-4403-b59e-cc6911e5a41a.6b352c61-7a84-45d6-b205-dacd2c800dd5.description=
Check to see if the value stored in a specified flow variable, denoted by key, is null.

Inputs\:
keyName - The key to check, i.e. the name of the flow variable.

Returns\: 
The value in the specified key, i.e. flow variable.

Responses\:
isNull - If the key is a null pointer, i.e. the flow variable doesn't have an assigned value.
notNull - If some value is stored in the key, i.e the flow variable has a value assigned.

Note that the inputs to this flow which correspond to web service inputs are optional inputs.  This is due to the fact that web services definitions usually incorrectly indicate that too many inputs are required, and mirroring those settings in the flow would force you to enter unused values when running the flow. auth_password - The input named efficientip_macro_add_ip_php|input|auth_password of the complex type\: efficientip_macro_add_ip_php|input

Responses\:
